{
  "stem": "18474.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The rounding us up, you know, and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, like they were taking us to work a lot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They appointed a few Jews, they called it the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And whenever they needed people, they just went to the Judenrat and--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Judenrat means like a-- like a-- they were the-- they were-- the Judenrat consisted of let's say four or five people from the town.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if they needed something, they didn't go to each individual, they went to the Judenrat and the Judenrat had to supply them this money people for work or this many people for this, whenever they needed.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember when they came in the first summer, right outside of town there was an airport which the Russians built and they bombed it when the war started.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were a lot of holes--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they attacked Russia, they bombed the airport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were a lot of holes there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they wanted to use it so they had to fill the holes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Right not far from us, there was a big building, they call it a palace-- we used to call it a palace.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so they dynamited it and they took so many Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were Germans with tractors and platforms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were taken over after they blew it up, take all that stuff on these platforms and they-- they used to bring it to fill in the holes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were working there on the-- on the ground for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, a lot of incidents happened while we were there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Life didn't mean nothing no more, like-- like I was telling you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll tell you a little incident what happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
